pageContext.claim: “Greg Murphy won big, 62% to 37%, in North Carolina 03, & the Fake News barely covered the race. The win was far bigger than anticipated - there was just nothing the Fakers could say to diminish or demean the scope of this victory.”
pageContext.analysis: Murphy was widely expected to win this heavily Republican district, and no forecast had him as close to his opponent as Trump falsely claims. His victory was widely reported, contrary to Trump's claim.
